OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPlenty of
OL,6,Fevening sunshine through this evening
OL,7,Fand remaining warm. Some cloud may
OL,8,Fpush in mainly to the east of the
OL,9,Fregion through the early hours of the
OL,10,Fmorning. Moderate easterly breeze.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FAny overnight cloud quickly
OL,13,Fclearing to leave a dry and sunny day
OL,14,Facross the region. Feeling very warm
OL,15,Fonce again. Brisk easterly winds
OL,16,Fpersisting.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
